'Yan majalisar Welsh sun damu cewa za su zama kamar Muppets
Wasu 'yan Majalisar (AM) sun yi mamakin shawarar da za a kira su a gaba' Member of the Welsh Parliament (MWP).
Wannan ya faru ne saboda shirin da aka yi na mayar da wannan majalisa zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
'Yan majalisa daga bangarorin siyasa daban-daban na damuwa da cewa za a iya yin watsi da su.
Wani dan majalisar daga jam'iyyar Labour ya bayyana cewa kungiyarsa tana damuwa da cewa sunan ya yi daidai da Twp da Pwp.
Ga masu karatu da ba 'yan Wales ba: a Welsh twp yana nufin "stupid" kuma pwp yana nufin "dumb".
Wani dan majalisar daga jam'iyyar Plaid Cymru ya bayyana cewa, "a matsayin duka, jam'iyyar ba ta gamsu ba" kuma ya ba da shawarar wasu hanyoyin magance matsalar.
Wani mai ra'ayin mazan jiya na kasar Wales ya ce kungiyarsa tana "buɗe" don a canja sunanta, amma MWP a jawabinsa na iya sauya zuwa Muppet.
A wannan mahallin, ana kiran harafin Welsh w kamar yadda ake furta harafin u a Turanci na Yorkshire.
Kwamitin majalisar da ke shirin tsara dokar sauya sunan ya bayyana cewa: Tabbas za a yanke hukunci a kan yadda za a nada wakilan majalisar su kansu.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta baiwa Majalisar Welsh ikon canza sunan ta.
A watan Yuni, kwamitin ya sanar da sakamakon shawarwarin jama'a game da shawarwarin da suka sami goyon baya mai yawa don canza sunan majalisar zuwa Welsh Parliament.
A lokacin da ya zo ga yadda za a kira 'yan majalisar wakilai, kwamitin ya fi son "Membobin Majalisar Welsh" ko MWPs, amma zaɓin MWP ya sami goyon baya mafi yawa a lokacin tattaunawar jama'a.
'Yan majalisar sun gabatar da wasu zabi, amma fafutukar neman matsaya daya zai iya janyo wa shugaban majalisar Elin Jones, wanda ake sa ran zai gabatar da kudurin sauye-sauyen a cikin 'yan makonni.
Dokar sake fasalin za ta hada da wasu canje-canje ga yadda majalisar ke aiki, gami da dokoki kan rashin cancantar wakilan majalisar da kuma kafa kwamitocin kwamiti.
A lokacin da ake tattauna dokar, 'yan majalisar za su yi zaɓe a kan yadda za a kira su.
