"Raba na biyu na zuba jari zai ninka damar da za a samu ci gaban AI a Amurka", in ji Lee a cikin wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa, "AI: China, Silicon Valley, and the New World Order", ya fito a wannan watan a gidan buga littattafai na Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne babban darektan kamfanin Sinovation Ventures, wanda ke zuba jari a cikin wani daga cikin manyan kamfanonin kera kere-kere na kasar Sin, Face++.
A cikin shekarun 1980s, a jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI wanda ya doke mafi kyawun ɗan wasan Amurka, Othello, kuma daga baya ya zama darektan bincike na Microsoft kuma shugaban reshen Google na China.
