Trump ya gudanar da wani taro a West Virginia, a tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara yakin neman zabensa da taron jama'a a Wheeling, West Virginia, a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin tarurruka biyar da aka shirya Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da ziyarar gajeren lokaci zuwa jihohin Tennessee da Mississippi.
Trump bai zabi sabon alƙali na Kotun Koli ba, kuma yana shirin ƙara yawan goyon baya a zaɓe mai zuwa saboda akwai haɗarin cewa 'yan Republican za su rasa rinjaye a Majalisar Dattijai bayan zaɓe na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a yammacin Virginia zai fara kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon shi a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, da karfe 7 na yammacin yammacin yamma, a ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron da Trump ya yi a West Virginia ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen bidiyo a kan YouTube.
A wannan makon ne dai, Trump zai yi tsokaci game da shari'ar da aka yi wa dan takarar kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wadda ta jawo cece-kuce kan zargin cin zarafin mata, wanda ya sa aka yi mako guda ana jiran amincewar majalisar dattawa, a yayin da ake ci gaba da binciken FBI.
Amma babban burin wannan taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su yi nasara a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Trump, an shirya wasu tarurruka guda biyar a mako mai zuwa don "sake jan hankalin masu ba da agaji da masu goyon baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin kiyayewa da kuma kara yawan 'yan majalisa da 'yan majalisar dokoki".
"Mafi rinjaye a Majalisa na da muhimmanci ga shirin shugaban da zai yi tafiya zuwa kasashe da dama yayin da muke shiga cikin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun kamfen din Trump da ba a bayyana sunansa ba.
Taron da za a yi a filin wasa na Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling da yammacin yau zai iya jawo hankalin magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, da kuma 'yan jarida daga Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar, Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin wata guda, inda ya lashe zaben 2016 da fiye da kashi 40 cikin dari.
A wani lokaci, Trump yana ƙoƙarin taimaka wa ɗan takarar majalisar dattijan Republican, Patrick Morrissey na West Virginia, wanda ke bin sahun masu jefa ƙuri'a.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban kasa ya kamata ya taimaka masa ya inganta a cikin kuri'un zabe", in ji masanin kimiyyar siyasa Simon Haedar na Jami'ar West Virginia ga kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
