To, wane ne ke da sa'a a wannan lokacin?
"Sun kasance da maki shida a gaba, yanzu sun zama hudu, don haka ina ganin cewa a yanzu, sa'a tana tare da mu", in ji Jordan Spieth a karshen ranar.
Turawa sun fice da maki huɗu, saura maki 12 a rage a wasan.
