Wannan jerin nasara da kuma irin karfin da ke tsakanin Fleetwood da Molinari sun nuna cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za a yi nasara a ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani dan wasan da ya fi su farin jini da zai iya cin nasarar 'yan Turai yayin da rana ke faɗuwa a filin wasan golf na Le National a birnin Paris.
Wataƙila su biyun za su yi nasara a lokaci ɗaya a wurare dabam-dabam.
Amma, a yanzu ya yi jinkirin yin magana game da nasarar da Turawa suka yi.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi saurin kashe Alex Noren da Sergio Garcia wanda ya yi fice a wasan na biyu da aka yi da safiya.
A wani rami guda da biyu a rami tara na farko a filin wasa, 'yan Spain da Sweden sun binne su a rami da ba su iya fitowa ba.
Amma, a ranar Lahadi, ba wanda zai taimaka wa mutane su fita daga cikin ransu.
Yana da ban sha'awa don kallon wasan kwaikwayo na biyu a kusa da ku saboda kuna iya ganin yadda 'yan wasan ke hulɗa a cikin nau'i-nau'i, ku ji abin da suke ba da shawara da wanda ba su ba, kuma ku yi nazarin dabarun da za a iya canzawa a cikin lokaci.
A halin yanzu, 'yan Turai sun fi juna iyawa a matsayin kungiya, kuma sun shiga ranar karshe da babbar nasara, amma wannan wasa a bangaren 'yan wasa biyu-biyu ya nuna cewa tawagar Amurka tana da karfin gwagwarmaya da wasu, musamman ma 'yan Stateside, suka yi shakkarsa.
'Yan wasan Turai sun shiga ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup da ta kai su da kashi goma da shida
A ranar Asabar, 'yan wasan Turai sun shiga wasan farko na Ryder Cup da tazarar da Amurka ta yi ta 10 zuwa 6.
Ƙungiyar 'yan wasa biyu, Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun yi nasara sau biyu a kan Tiger Woods, wanda ya kai gasar Le Golf National da ta kai ta maki huɗu.
'Yan wasan Turai Thomas Bjorn a kokarinsa na lashe kofin da ya rasa a Hazeltine shekara biyu da suka gabata sun fi 'yan wasan Amurka a wasannin da suka yi a safiyar yau, inda suka ci 3-1.
Aikin da 'yan wasan Amurka suka yi a wasan biyu-biyu ya nuna cewa sun fi juna ƙarfi, amma sun riga sun yi nasara sosai a wasan.
Don lashe kofin, 'yan wasan Jim Furyck suna bukatar su tara maki takwas a wasanni 12 da ake yi a ranar Lahadi.
Fleetwood shi ne dan wasa na farko a gasar Turai da ya ci kwallo hudu a jere, shi da Molinari, wanda aka fi sani da Molliwood, sun zama ma'aurata biyu da suka ci kwallo hudu a wasan da aka yi a gasar Ryder Cup bayan wasan da ya yi fice a makon jiya.
