Zinke ya ce, shigar da Rasha cikin Syria - musamman inda take aiki a lokacin da take aiki a lokacin da gwamnati ta amince da ita - wani dalili ne na neman sabbin kasuwanni na makamashi.
"Na yi imanin cewa dalilin da ya sa Rasha ke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne saboda tana son sayar da makamashi a yankin kamar yadda take yi a Gabashin Turai, yankin kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Amma a ganinsa, akwai hanyoyi da kuma hanyoyin da za a iya magance wannan matsalar.
Amurka tare da taimakon sojan ruwa na iya samar da hanyoyin ruwa da kuma toshewa, idan ya zama dole, don tabbatar da cewa makamashin su bai isa kasuwa ba, in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi jawabi ne a taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya wanda ya nuna cewa ita ce "muryar masu amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta yadda Washington ke tunkarar Rasha da Iran, ya nuna cewa duk daya ne.
"Zaɓin tattalin arzikin Iran da Rasha ya fi ko ƙasa da amfani da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yayin da a kan Rasha, ya ce "ana amfani da wannan dabara" a cikin tattalin arzikin mai mai mai da man fetur.
Sanarwar ta zo ne a daidai lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ke shirin kara fitar da iskar gas dinta zuwa Turai, inda za ta maye gurbin Rasha da wani abu mai rahusa ga masu amfani da shi a Turai.
A wannan bangaren, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump da kansa, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga "kwakkwarar" aikin Nord Stream 2, wanda, a cewar Trump, ya sanya Berlin "kwaryar" Moscow.
Moscow ta sha nanata cewa aikin gas din na Nord Stream 2 mai darajar dala biliyan 11, wanda zai ninka karfin gas din da ake da shi na zamani zuwa mita miliyan 110, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
A cewar gwamnatin Kremlin, tsananin adawa da gwamnatin Washington ke yi wa wannan aikin, ya samo asali ne daga dalilai na tattalin arziki, kuma hakan ya nuna rashin adalci ne.
"Na yi imanin cewa mun yarda cewa ba za a yi amfani da makamashi a matsayin hanyar yin amfani da makamashi ba, kuma ya kamata a bai wa masu amfani da makamashi damar zabar masu kawo su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha, Aleksandr Novak, bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka, Rick Perry, a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Matsayin Amurka ya jawo martani daga Jamus wadda ta sake jaddada kudurinta ga aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, BDI, ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta guji manufofin makamashi na EU da kuma yarjejeniyar da aka kulla tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a cikin samar mana da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI), bayan wani taron da shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel ta yi da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren za ta "yi tunani sosai" game da neman takarar shugabancin kasa a 2020, a cewar 'yar majalisar dattijai ta Massachusetts
'Yar majalisar dattijai Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta "yi la'akari da" neman takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar shekara.
A wani taron da ta yi da jama'a a garin Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta tabbatar da cewa tana tunanin tsayawa takarar.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan na bukatar mace a kan mulki", in ji ta, kamar yadda The Hill ta ruwaito.
"Bayan 6 ga Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari da zabar kaina a matsayin shugaban kasa".
Warren ya yi tsokaci game da Shugaba Donald Trump a yayin da yake ganawa da jama'a, yana mai cewa yana jagorantar kasarsa zuwa inda ba daidai ba.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokradiyyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ta yi magana a bainar jama'a game da Trump da kuma dan takararsa na kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
A wani sakon da ta wallafa a shafinta na Twitter ranar Juma'a, Warren ta ce: "Hakika muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin a kada kuri'a".
Sai dai kuma, wani zaben da aka gudanar a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin masu son Warren ba sa ganin ya kamata ta fito takara a 2020.
A wani bincike da cibiyar bincike kan siyasa ta jami'ar Suffolk ta Boston Globe ta gudanar, kashi hamsin da takwas na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata ta yi takara ba.
Kashi talatin da biyu ne suka goyi bayan takarar.
Kuri'ar da aka gudanar ta nuna cewa, tsohon gwamnan jihar, Deval Patrick, ya fi kowa goyon baya, inda kashi 38 cikin 100 suka ce zai iya tsayawa takara, kuma kashi 48 suka ce ba zai iya tsayawa ba.
Sauran manyan sunayen 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat da aka tattauna game da yiwuwar yin takarar shugaban kasa a 2020 sune tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa Joe Biden da Sanata Bernie Sanders na Vermont.
Biden ya ce zai yanke hukunci a hukumance a watan Janairu, kamar yadda kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya ruwaito.
Sarah Palin ta ambaci PTSP ta hanyar Palin a taron Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26 ya yi shekara guda a Iraqi bayan ya shiga aikin soja a watan Satumba.
An kama shi da laifin aikata laifukan da suka shafi cin zarafin mata da 'ya'yansu da suka faru a ranar Litinin da daddare.
"Abin da ɗana yake fuskanta, abin da yake fuskanta bayan dawowa, ya yi daidai da sauran iyalai da ke fama da PTSD da sauran raunin da sojojinmu ke fama da shi", ta fada wa masu sauraro a taron Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ya kira kama shi da wata matsala da ba a magana a kai ba kuma ga ɗanta da sauran tsoffin sojoji ya ce "suna dawowa da ɗan bambanci, suna dawowa da ƙarfi, suna dawowa suna mamakin ko akwai girmamawa ga abin da sauran sojoji da matukan jirgin sama, da sauran membobin sojojin, suka bayar ga wannan ƙasa. "
An kama shi a Wasilla, Alaska a ranar Litinin, aka tuhume shi da laifin cin zarafin mata, hana yin rahoton cin zarafin mata, da kuma mallakar makami a cikin maye, in ji Dan Bennett, mai magana da yawun 'yan sanda a Wasilla.
Jihohi 18 da DC sun goyi bayan sake duba sabuwar manufar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da kuma gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan wata doka da ta kalubalanci wata sabuwar manufa ta Amurka da ta hana 'yan gudun hijira mafaka daga 'yan bindiga da kuma cin zarafin gidaje.
Wakilan jihohi da gundumomi 18 sun gabatar da rahoto a ranar Juma'a a Washington don ba da goyon baya ga mai neman mafaka da ke kalubalantar manufofin, in ji NBC News.
An dai bayyana cikakken sunayen wadanda suka shigar da kara a kan Grace Sessions wanda kungiyar kare hakkin jama'a ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta, inda ta yi tir da manufofin gwamnatin tarayya.
Ta ce mijinta da kuma 'yan kungiyarsa sun ci zarafinta, amma jami'an Amurka sun ki ba ta mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
An kama ta a jihar Texas.
Lauyoyin da suka goyi bayan Grace sun bayyana kasashen El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, wadanda suka fi yawan wadanda suka nemi mafaka a Amurka, a matsayin kasashen da ke fuskantar matsalar da ake samu a ko'ina ta 'yan bindiga da kuma cin zarafin cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka a Amurka ta sauya shawarar da Kwamitin Shige da Fice na Amurka ya yanke a shekarar 2014 wanda ya ba da damar baƙi marasa takardu da ke gujewa tashin hankali a cikin gida su nemi mafaka.
Babban Lauyan gundumar Columbia Karl Racine ya ce a cikin jawabinsa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabon manufar "ya yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa".
Dokar tarayya ta ce duk wani bukatar neman mafaka za a yi shi ne bisa ga ainihin abubuwan da suka faru da kuma yanayin da ake tuhuma, kuma irin wannan cikas ya saba wa wannan ka'ida, in ji rahoton na Abokan Kotu.
Lauyoyi sun ci gaba da cewa manufofin hana shigar da baƙi suna cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna da'awar cewa sun fi iya zama 'yan kasuwa da' yan kasuwa da kuma 'samun ma'aikata da ake buƙata'.
Babban lauya Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalai da su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke gudun hijira daga tashin hankali da kuma ƙungiyoyin 'yan bindiga a watan Yuni.
"Ayyukan mafaka na samuwa ga wadanda suka bar gidajensu saboda zalunci ko kuma fargabar tsere saboda launin fata, addini, 'yan kasa ko kuma kasancewarsu na wata kungiya ko ra'ayin siyasa", Sessions ya ce a sanarwar da ya fitar a ranar 11 ga watan Yuni.
Ba a taɓa yin nufin mafaka ba ne don ya magance dukan matsalolin da mutane suke fuskanta a ko'ina a duniya a kullum, ko ma waɗanda suke da tsanani.
