Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da "ta'addanci" ta hanyar "tallace-tallace"
Mako guda bayan jaridar hukuma ta kasar Sin ta wallafa wata takarda mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke tallata cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da yin amfani da jaridar Amurka don yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump a ranar Laraba ya yi tir da wani karin kudin da ake biyan manema labarai na China Daily a jaridar Des Moines Register, wadda ita ce jaridar da ta fi yawan sayarwa a Iowa, bayan da ya zargi China da cewa tana son ta tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, abin da China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka bayyana a wata sanarwa da suka fitar wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters, a matsayin wani sabon mataki na kamfen na Washington na matsa wa China lamba.
Duk da cewa ba sabon abu ba ne ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su sanya tallace-tallace don inganta cinikayya, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin yakin cinikayya mai tsanani wanda ya haifar da hauhawar harajin shigo da kayayyaki.
China ta dauki mataki a farkon yakin cinikayya da aka tsara don kai hari ga masu fitar da kaya a jihohin kamar Iowa wanda ya goyi bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, a cewar masana na kasar Sin da na Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa na tsawon lokaci, babban mai fitar da kayan gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanonin Amurka.
A wata kasida a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register ta ranar Lahadi, Branstad ya ce kasar Sin "a yanzu ta kara wannan cin zarafi ta hanyar tura tallace-tallace a cikin jaridarmu ta 'yanci".
"Ta hanyar yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin China ta yi amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da' yanci na 'yan jarida ta hanyar sanya talla a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A bangare guda, a wani kantin sayar da jaridu a kan titunan Beijing za ku ga ƙarancin muryoyin adawa kuma ba za ku ga wani ainihin nuna bambancin ra'ayoyi da mutanen China za su iya yi ba game da matsalar tattalin arzikin China saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin matsin lamba daga Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta Sin", ya rubuta.
Ya kara da cewa, "wasu daga cikin manyan jaridun kasar Sin sun ki amincewa da buga labarin na, ko da yake bai bayyana ko wace jaridar aka yi ba".
'Yan Republican sun yi amfani da Kavanaugh wajen janye mata daga zaben, in ji masu sharhi
Da yake 'yan jam'iyyar Republican da dama sun goyi bayan dan takarar da zai zama alkalin kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, suna kare shi a kan zargin da ake masa na cin zarafin mata, 'yan sharhi sun yi gargadin cewa wannan zai haifar da mummunan sakamako a lokacin zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, musamman ga mata.
Juyayin da aka yi a wannan taron ya yi yawa, kuma 'yan Republican da dama sun riga sun nuna cewa suna son su ci gaba da jefa ƙuri'a.
Irin wannan ba za a iya dawowa ba, in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya nuna shakkunsa cewa, na karshe na Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) na son gudanar da binciken FBI zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu zaɓe masu fushi.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, ba za su manta da shi gobe ba, ko a watan Nuwamba", Karine Jean-Pierre, babbar mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar masu ci gaba MoveOn a kasar, ta ce a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington, D.C.
A safiyar yau Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun yi waƙar "Ku zo nan, ku yi sanyi!" suna zanga-zangar a zauren majalisar dattawa yayin da 'yan Republican da ke iko da Kwamitin Shari'a ke shirin ci gaba da zaben Kavanaugh duk da shaidar da Dr. Christine Blasey Ford ta bayar, in ji rahoton Mic.
"Kamar yadda aka saba, za a samu farin ciki da kuma kwarin gwiwa a jam'iyyar Democrat", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai sharhi kan harkokin siyasa da ba ya goyon bayan wani bangare a jam'iyyar.
Mutane suna cewa sun riga sun kai matakin da ya kamata, kuma hakan gaskiya ne.
Amma za su iya zama mafi girma, musamman a tsakanin mata a cikin unguwannin da ke kewaye da su da kuma matasa masu jefa ƙuri'a, daga 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda duk da cewa ba sa son shugaban, amma ba sa yawan jefa ƙuri'a.
Ko da kafin a ba da shaidar da aka yi wa Ford, wadda ta yi bayani dalla-dalla game da zargin da ta yi na cin zarafin mata da dan takarar kujerar kotun koli, manazarta na cewa, 'yan Republican za su iya fuskantar mummunan sakamako idan suka ci gaba da ikirarin.
"Wannan babban abin takaici ne ga Tsohon Jam'iyyar", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a farkon makon da ya gabata, kamar yadda NBC News ta ruwaito.
"Ba wai kawai batun kuri'un kwamitin ko na karshe ba, ko kuma an tura Kavanaugh a kan kujerar, amma kuma yadda 'yan Republican suka yi amfani da shi da kuma yadda suka bi da shi", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan kungiyar Priorities USA, wata kungiya mai taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat.
Amma, da alama Amurkawa sun ɗan rarrabu kan wanda za su yarda da shi bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, tare da ɗan ƙara nuna son kai ga Ford.
Sabon zaben da kamfanin YouGov ya fitar ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun tabbata ko kuma sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 suka ce sun tabbata ko sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin 100 sun ce sun yi imanin cewa Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin 100 kawai suka ce hakan ga Ford.
Bayan matsin lamba daga Flake, FBI a halin yanzu suna binciken da'awar da Ford ya yi, tare da aƙalla wata mai gabatar da kara, Deborah Ramirez, The Guardian ta ruwaito.
A gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa, a makon da ya gabata, Ford ta ba da shaida a karkashin rantsuwa cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade a lokacin da take da shekaru 17.
Ramirez ta ce wani da take nema a matsayin babban mai shari'a ya nuna mata al'aurarsa a wani liyafa a lokacin da take karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro gidan yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin kafa sabuwar intanet da za ta kwace Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya fara wani sabon kamfani da ke neman ya yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin wannan mashahurin fasahar, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke haɓaka a kan dandalin buɗewa na Berners-Lee, Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma mutanen da za a ba su damar samun damar wasu bayanai.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi ba'a game da manufar da ke bayan wannan kutse na " mamayar duniya. "
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi, yana nufin kamfanin da ya fara.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar  keɓaɓɓen gidan yanar gizon ajiyar bayanai ko POD.
Za su iya ɗauke da jerin sunayen abokan hulɗarsu, jerin abubuwan da za su yi, kalandar, laburaren kiɗa, da kuma wasu abubuwa na kansu da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna nan a kan wani mai bincike a lokaci guda.
Abu daya da ke da banbanci game da adana bayanan sirri a yanar gizo shi ne, yanke shawara kan wanda zai iya samun dama ga wane bayani na mai amfani ne.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "karfafawa ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar shugaban kamfanin John Bruce, ita ce kamfanin ya samar da albarkatu, tsari da kuma kwarewa don taimakawa wajen samar da Solid ga kowa.
Kamfanin yanzu ya kunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani tsarin tsaro da IBM ta saya, da wasu injiniyoyi da suka sanya hannu a kan yarjejeniyar yin aiki a kan aikin, da kuma al'ummar masu shirye-shirye da suka ba da kansu.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka a duk faɗin duniya sun sami damar gina aikace-aikacen aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa tattaunawa da Facebook da Google kan ko za su yi wani canji na musamman wanda zai sauya dukkan tsarin kasuwancin su gaba daya.
Ba ma neman izinin su.
A wata sanarwa da ya wallafa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Inrupt na da "tayin aiki na samar da makamashi da kuma tsarin halittu na kasuwanci don kare mutuncin da ingancin sabuwar hanyar sadarwa da aka gina a kan Solidium".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sake fasalin yanar gizo lokacin da ya kafa gidan yanar gizo mai suna World Wide Web a Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT).
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka-tsakin yanar gizo.
Ko da ya fara Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma ya jagoranci World Wide Web Consortium, da World Wide Web Foundation da kuma Open Data Institute.
"Ina matuƙar farin ciki game da zamanin yanar gizo na gaba", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: Godiya ga ba da kyautar Victoria Cross ga firistoci daga Yaƙin Duniya na ɗaya
Bikin girmama limamin cocin Ingila wanda ya sami lambar Victoria Cross a lokacin yakin duniya na farko ya gudana a garin da aka haife shi shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
Lt. Hon. Bernard Vann ya sami lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 a cikin harin da aka kai a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma bayan kwana huɗu sai aka kashe shi da wani maharbi, kuma bai san cewa an ba shi lambar yabo mafi girma a ƙasar Britaniya ba.
'Ya'yan jikokinsa biyu ne suka gano dutsen a wani bikin biki a Rushden, Northamptonshire, ranar Asabar.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce yana da "alamar mamaki" cewa za a gano dutsen shekara 100 bayan da aka gano kakansa wanda ya sa aka ba shi wannan lambar yabo.
A wani rahoto da jaridar London Gazette ta wallafa, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Col. Vann ya ja-goranci rundunarsa ta ratsa mashigin St. Quentin a cikin "ƙari mai dimbin yawa da kuma ƙarar da ake yi a kan filin daga da kuma injin-dakin da ake kai hari.
Daga baya ya shiga cikin sahun gaba kuma tare da "babban ƙarfin hali" ya jagoranci tawagar zuwa gaba kafin ya yi tsalle a kan bindiga na Poland ba tare da taimako ba kuma ya kashe mutane uku daga cikin rundunar.
Wani ɗan harbi na Jamus ya kashe Lieutenant Colonel Vann a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, wato, wata ɗaya kafin a daina yaƙin.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce abin da kakansa ya yi ya zama "abin da na sani ba zan taɓa yi ba", kuma hakan ya sa ya zama mai tawali'u.
